        "kind": "pull_request",
        "title": "refactor: centralize skills subsystem",
        "body": "## Summary\n\nThis refactors OpenClaw skills code into a dedicated `src/skills` subsystem while preserving existing runtime behavior.\n\nThe change moves skill discovery, loading, runtime snapshot handling, lifecycle/install logic, remote refresh paths, upload handling, shared types, and test support out of scattered agent/gateway/infra locations. External callers now import the specific skills component they need from `src/skills/...`, while `src/skills/index.ts` stays a small intentional facade.\n\nBehavior is intended to remain unchanged:\n- existing `<available_skills>` prompt/catalog behavior is preserved;\n- existing skill snapshot hydration and freshness behavior is preserved;\n- preloaded skill snapshot entries are preserved;\n- empty skill filters keep their previous short-circuit behavior;\n- install, ClawHub, upload, remote, CLI, gateway, auto-reply, cron, and session paths continue calling the same underlying behavior through the centralized subsystem.\n\nThis also narrows the existing `skills/` oxlint ignore so the new `src/skills` subsystem is linted as part of core checks.\n\n## Verification\n\n- `git diff --check`\n- Local focused branch validation: 49 files / 486 tests passed\n- Prior Testbox-through-Crabbox focused validation `tbx_01kssmerwt49mvcvwk48p72qqy`: 49 files / 486 tests passed\n- Testbox-through-Crabbox changed gate `tbx_01kssy946ckpkbev0dm9qkhysv`: `pnpm check:changed && pnpm test:changed`\n  - `pnpm check:changed` passed, including `src/skills` linting over 81 files\n  - `pnpm test:changed` passed 490 files / 7267 tests and failed 7 tests in `src/agents/embedded-agent-runner/model.test.ts`\n  - The branch does not modify `src/agents/embedded-agent-runner/model.test.ts` or `src/agents/embedded-agent-runner/model.ts`\n- Focused rerun of the failed file passed locally: `pnpm test src/agents/embedded-agent-runner/model.test.ts` (99 tests passed)\n- Focused rerun of the failed file passed on Testbox-through-Crabbox `tbx_01kssz73aa80qg6y6kqe8t1pfh`: `pnpm test src/agents/embedded-agent-runner/model.test.ts` (99 tests passed)\n- Auto-review completed with no accepted actionable findings\n- Manual live smoke against an OCM dev-watch env:\n  - natural weather prompt exposed and used the `weather` skill capability\n  - natural X/Twitter monitoring prompt exposed and used the `xforme-social-agent` capability\n  - both confirmed the existing skill catalog behavior is still active\n",
